## Risks & Blockers

| Risk | Mitigation |
|---|---|
| LinkedIn access tokens expire (60 days) and **cannot be refreshed** without the `r_liteprofile` refresh flow | We check `isTokenExpired()` and show a "Reconnect" banner. Users re-auth when token expires. |
| `/v2/ugcPosts` requires `w_member_social` scope which must be explicitly granted by LinkedIn App review | User has confirmed "Share on LinkedIn" product is enabled — scope is available |
| Database tables don't exist yet | Output `.sql` file — user must run it before testing |
| `.env.local` has no actual LinkedIn credentials filled in | User must fill `LINKEDIN_CLIENT_ID` and `LINKEDIN_CLIENT_SECRET` before OAuth works |
| The existing `page.tsx` at `/dashboard/linkedin` is 446 lines of hardcoded demo — full overwrite needed | We overwrite with `Overwrite: true`, preserving no demo code |
| LangChain `getModel()` returns `ChatGoogleGenerativeAI` — we need to `.invoke()` with `HumanMessage` | Follows the pattern already used in `lib/ai/email-analyzer.ts` |

